                        <div class="prose prose-lg text-gray-700">
                            <p>The National Certificate: Farming (NQF Level 1) provides foundational knowledge and skills in general agricultural practices. This qualification is designed for individuals entering the agricultural sector with a broad focus on farming operations.</p>
                            <p>Students will gain practical skills in crop production, farm management, agricultural business principles, and safety practices while developing essential communication and mathematical literacy skills.</p>
